comment.author: 25695066@N00
comment._content: Note, the F-14A Tomcat in the background, while wearing US markings, is actually one the 80 Tomcats ordered by the Shah of Iran (delivered as IIAF 3-6010, later re-serialed as IRIAF  3-6040 / ex- BuNo 160338).  79 Tomcats would ultimately be delivered to Iran (including the one in this photo) before the Shah was deposed in 1979.
